Now that you understand the real mechanics behind Web3 Wallet Connect, it's time to take action. Start by integrating the solution into your digital store and test it with a few customers. Use the Admin Dashboard to monitor your sales and transaction logs. Make sure to set up accurate pricing conversions and support for the cryptocurrencies your customers prefer. Once you've implemented Web3 Wallet Connect, you'll be able to get paid instantly for your digital products, without any intermediaries or KYC requirements."
  ],
  "paa_response": "The most common question creators like you have is 'Will I need to set up a PayPal or Stripe account to use Web3 Wallet Connect?' The answer is no. Web3 Wallet Connect uses NOWPayments as its payment processor, which supports over 300 coins and doesn't require any KYC or buyer account setup.
